data.description: RARE!!!  TWO LOTS available SIDE-BY-SIDE 221030831 & 221030806.  Desirable SOUTHERN EXPOSURE!!!  Together these lots would make a beautiful big home site.  Vacant Lots located in up and coming area west of Old Burnt Store Road in unit 90. Short drive to shopping, Gulf Access Boat Ramp, Restaurants and more… Located in the City of Cape Coral's New Vision planning area with lots of beautiful new construction homes nearby. Imagine building your dream home in this beautiful golf neighborhood. Now that is living the Paradise dream.... Or keep as an INVESTMENT as we watch the City continue to grow!!! Saltwater Boating Access from several Community Boat Ramps located throughout the city will give you access to the Gulf of Mexico, beaches, and surrounding islands such as Cayo Costa, Cabbage Key, Sanibel, Boca Grand... Not to mention...this area offers some of the best fishing to be found anywhere in the world. Plus, you'll love the fact that this lot is only about 37 miles to the Fort Myers Int'l Airport, 16 miles to the Punta Gorda Airport, 4 miles to Coral Oaks Golf Course, and 6 miles to the Burnt Store BOAT RAMP! Call today!
